    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 3rd level, your study into the art of verbal degradation has expanded your mental prowess.</p><p> You gain proficiency in Performance, Persuasion, and Deception.</p><p> Also, you may use Wisdom to calculate your Armor Class.</p><p> At 6th level, once per round, you gain one Superiority Die when you either: Pass a skill check that benefits from Slander, a target fails a save against a Genjutsu boosted by Amp, or you Suprise a target with Subliminal Messaging.</p><p></p>",
